event.title: Fellowship Meeting Rhine/Main - Talk: Freie Software Lizenzen

body.p: On Wednesday, 2 March, the Fellowship group Rhein/Main will meet in "Zentrale Coworking" in Frankfurt to attend a talk by Michael Stehmann titled "Freie Software Lizenzen". We will meet there around 19:00 h, the talk will start at 19:30.
